  <span id="freeText17084079741711891564" style="display:none">This sequel of 'From Man To Man' is excellent,<br /><br />To say that I thoroughly enjoyed 'It Began With Ashes' would be an understatement .... the characters of Draven, his friends and their families have really firmed up in my imagination and I can really picture them.<br /><br />I would have no hesitation in recommending this book to anyone who likes the combination of Historical Fiction, Action, Adventure and a light touch of Fantasy.<br /><br />I look forward to the next book of this series 'A Stirring Of Dead Embers'<br /><br />See my review also at:<br /><br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.amazon.co.uk/product-reviews/B00ACLW7TO/ref=cm_cr_pr_top_recent?ie=UTF8&amp;showViewpoints=0&amp;sortBy=bySubmissionDateDescending">http://www.amazon.co.uk/product-revie...</a><br /><br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.amazon.com/product-reviews/B00ACLW7TO/ref=cm_cr_pr_top_recent?ie=UTF8&amp;showViewpoints=0&amp;sortBy=bySubmissionDateDescending">http://www.amazon.com/product-reviews...</a></span>
